        <heading>2783. Assignable and heritable rights and obligations</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2783. Assignable and heritable rights and obligations
In the absence of a contrary provision of law or juridical act, the rights and obligations of the parties under an annuity contract are assignable and heritable.</p>
        </content>
